

#### ECE670-System Software Design _Project #####
#### Multi-Threaded Webserver ###################


To compile the design : 
>> make server 

To Run the design : 
>> make run 


The server run on port no 9000 


To test the Webserver - using the httperf use the following command. 
1. set the Server to IP address of the machine that the WEbserver is runnin on, in tahis case it is 10.0.0.1
2. Port no is the port that webserver is configured with. 
3. num-conn : Number of connection 
4. Rate defines the rate at which the connection are made. 

>> httperf --server=10.0.0.1 --port=9000 --wlog=Y,html/tempfiles/url.log --num-conn=1000 --timeout=10 --rate=100





